data.description: Ready to start new in the new year? Come see this cute ranch with lots of special touches throughout! Pull up to a large sweeping front yard with a charming home at the top of the hill. Step inside to on-trend paint colors in a living room with soaring cathedral ceilings and bright white baseboards. Arched entries make for special touches with a pass-through to the kitchen and tons of natural light. Cozy up to the fireplace with stone accents. Open concept dining room is ready to entertain friends for the holidays with outdoor access for lots of light. Wait, did we mention the gorgeous and easy-to-maintain wood look tile floors throughout the entire home? NO carpet! Step through the archway to the kitchen featuring a beautiful stainless steel gas range/oven and lots of counter space as well as a bright and airy breakfast room. At the end of the day, retreat to the spacious and bright primary bedroom with an en-suite bath with dual sinks, separate garden tub, and walk-in shower. Across the house, for maximum privacy, are 2 generous secondary bedrooms and a full bath. Enjoy evenings outside in the backyard with a patio slab and wooded views! Conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants, parks and recreation. No HOA Easy rental!
